                                    <img src="/images/foods/Rock_Oysters.jpg" class="w-100 rounded">
                                </div>
                                <div class="food-title">
                                    <span class="font-weight-bold">石蚵料理</span>
                                    <span class="en">Rock Oysters</span>
                                </div>
                            </a>
                        </div>
                        <div class="col-lg-4 col-md-6 food-item">
                            <a href="/foods/5">
                                <div class="food-info">
                                    淋上蛋汁的鍋貼底部煎的焦黃酥脆，咬下一口蛋香四溢的鍋貼，感受內餡微帶肉汁在嘴裡蔓延的鮮甜滋味，再點上酸辣湯和其他特色小吃，簡直是一大享受。
                                </div>
                                <div class="food-img">
                                    <img src="/images/foods/Potstickers.jpg" class="w-100 rounded">
                                </div>
                                <div class="food-title">
                                    <span class="font-weight-bold">鍋貼</span>
                                    <span class="en">Potstickers </span>
                                </div>
